      <title>PayPal 支持 PYUSD 稳定币用于 Xoom 跨境汇款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/paypal-s-pyusd-stablecoin-now-available-for-xoom-cross-border-money-transfers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[PayPal Holdings Inc. 的 Xoom 跨境汇款服务现在允许客户使用 PayPal 美元稳定币兑换的美元向国外汇款，这是加密货币侵蚀国际汇款的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/paypal-s-pyusd-stablecoin-now-available-for-xoom-cross-border-money-transfers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 16:56:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着云调查的增多，微软面临南非的投诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/microsoft-faces-south-african-complaint-as-cloud-probes-multiply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于世界各地监管机构越来越担心这家美国科技巨头滥用其市场力量排挤竞争对手，微软公司的 Azure 云业务将受到南非反垄断监管机构的正式投诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/microsoft-faces-south-african-complaint-as-cloud-probes-multiply</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 16:48:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>路透社称 Alphabet 正在与顾问讨论 HubSpot 交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/alphabet-talking-with-advisers-about-hubspot-deal-reuters-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据路透社周四报道，Alphabet Inc. 正在与财务顾问讨论可能对 HubSpot Inc. 提出收购要约的事宜，HubSpot Inc. 是一家价值约 340 亿美元的在线营销软件公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/alphabet-talking-with-advisers-about-hubspot-deal-reuters-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 14:18:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国官员就中国芯片限制向荷兰政府施压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/us-officials-to-pressure-dutch-government-on-china-chip-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着拜登政府加大力度挫败北京的科技野心，美国高级官员计划下周访问荷兰，向荷兰政府施压，要求其加强对中国芯片设备的限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/us-officials-to-pressure-dutch-government-on-china-chip-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 14:15:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Activist Fund Sachem 负责人将增持 Delivery Hero 股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/activist-fund-sachem-head-said-to-build-stake-in-delivery-hero</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，激进投资者 Sachem Head Capital Management 已持有 Delivery Hero SE 3.6% 的股份，并可能寻求在这家德国食品配送公司的董事会中担任代表。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/activist-fund-sachem-head-said-to-build-stake-in-delivery-hero</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 13:01:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊投资者希望随着现金储备的增加获得更大的回报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/amazon-investors-eye-swelling-cash-pile-with-stock-near-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多年来，亚马逊公司一直是科技巨头中向股东返还资金最吝啬的。现在，它产生了如此多的现金，以至于华尔街的一些人预计会获得更丰厚的回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/amazon-investors-eye-swelling-cash-pile-with-stock-near-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 11:07:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特拉维夫 GPS 扰乱，以色列等待伊朗报复性袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/tel-aviv-gps-is-scrambled-over-fears-of-iran-revenge-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，以色列扰乱了特拉维夫都会区的导航信号，为应对伊朗可能对经济中心的袭击做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/tel-aviv-gps-is-scrambled-over-fears-of-iran-revenge-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 08:44:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德表示，世界一流的肯尼亚股票仍然具有价值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/kenya-stocks-blackrock-says-world-s-best-performer-offers-value</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的资产管理公司贝莱德 (BlackRock Inc.) 看到了投资肯尼亚股票的机会，肯尼亚股票已从 2023 年全球表现最差的股票跃升至今年表现最好的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/kenya-stocks-blackrock-says-world-s-best-performer-offers-value</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 07:01:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Twilio 在活动人士压力下寻求董事会任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/twilio-asks-investors-to-back-new-board-terms-deeter-to-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受到激进投资者挑战的软件公司 Twilio Inc. 要求股东从 2025 年开始将董事会董事任期从三年改为一年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/twilio-asks-investors-to-back-new-board-terms-deeter-to-exit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 00:13:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
